We can use diffrent tools to check if the server is vulnerable to XSS or not. 


Option 1) XSStrike :- Download and install it 
                    git clone https://github.com/s0md3v/XSStrike.git
                    cd XSStrike
                    pip install -r requirements.txt
                    python xsstrike.py -u "http://SERVER_IP:PORT/index.php?task=test" 

Note :- When we want to run this, we can Network tools to get the path of th URL. Update the parameters with test 
        e.g http://94.237.54.42:39155/?fullname=asd&username=sad&password=asd&email=safd%40dsf.com

Option 2) Brute XSS


Option 3) XSSer
